    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
　唯今肥後邸ニ横井を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">尋</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（たづね）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>候所、夜前申合候通、伏<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">水</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（見）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ニ<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">相待</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（あひまつ）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と申て、今日八ツ時頃、出足ニて候よし。<lb />
　<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">下拙</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（げせつ）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ニ於ても一言、神戸へまて<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">申遣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（まうしつかは）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>し<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">度儀</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（たきぎ）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">有<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>之</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（これあり）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>、又先刻御談申せし儀も有て、薩邸ニも早々<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">参多</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（まゐりた）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>し。<lb />
　故ニ今夜伏水ニ下り明朝上京と存付候間、吉井への状一封今夜中、何卒御遣しの程<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">奉<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>希</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（ねがひたてまつる）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>。<lb />
<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">頓首々</span>
<span rend="jisage_4" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 4em">八日</span>
<span rend="chitsuki_2" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 2em">花押</span>
<span rend="chitsuki_3" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 3em">坂本龍馬</span>
<span rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">村田巳三郎様<span rend="chitsuki_4" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 4em">直陰</span></span>
<span rend="jisage_6" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 6em">足下</span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
